message.content:
cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as bilingual lexicon induction and caption modeling. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper utilizes images and their associated captions to learn the lexicon induction. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a multi-lingual caption model trained with different mono-lingual multimodal data to map words in different languages into joint spaces. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with unsupervised learning of word representations. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with multimodal data (images and captions) for bilingual lexicon induction.
